    <sec>
      <title>Conclusion</title>
      <p>This case indicates that Primary Multifocal OHL may present in childhood. It demonstrates the difficulties in reaching a definitive diagnosis, and the need to continually evaluate patients and diagnoses, especially when patients fail to respond to initial therapies.</p>
